snippet: Facing the Seahawks in Seattle, the Jets will be playing in what Rex Ryan considers “about as tough a venue as there is in the National Football League.”
abstract: New York Jets are preparing to face Seattle Seahawks at CenturyLink Field in Seattle, where fan noise is major drawback for visiting teams.
lead_paragraph: Facing the Seahawks in Seattle, the Jets will be playing in what Rex Ryan considers “about as tough a venue as there is in the National Football League.”

headline.seo: Jets Headed to Meet Seahawks at Stadium Tough on Visitors
headline.main: Jets Bound for Stadium That’s Known for Noise
headline.print_headline: Jets Bound for Stadium That’s Known for Noise
